column6: Aquí es donde se entrena la infantería de élite que sirve a los señores judios. Se pone especial atención en equipar a los soldados con la mejor armadura que el dinero pueda comprar. column2: The “Campus Martius” (or field of mars) is where military training for legionaries is carried out. Traditionally the training consisted of using training weapons that were much heavier than the actual weapon. The recruits place a stake in the training field and attack it as if it were an enemy. Commoners will generally come and spurn the young men on with cheering as well.
